ca, who had dropped the baton, were vying for the lesser medals.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Amber Anning timed her run to perfection to take the final step of the podium.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, it meant Britain have won a medal in all five relays with five individual medals also in their athletics haul.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7355580946917463, \"rank\": 0.3595019416742084, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2076, \"end\": 2085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999994040549111, \"rank\": 5.806034830220275e-07, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource